In a restaurant, the waiter
comes and takes your order

00:37:01.380 --> 00:37:06.630
first, but I sort of did it
the other way around here.

00:37:06.630 --> 00:37:09.100
Well, let's say I gave
you the appetizers,

00:37:09.100 --> 00:37:14.130
and now, you can
place your order,

00:37:14.130 --> 00:37:17.180
if you want to hear more
