which is coming from the atma.

00:38:08.580 --> 00:38:15.640
And when the atma
leaves the body--

00:38:15.640 --> 00:38:20.590
I've described the ideal, that
it goes to the spiritual realm.

00:38:20.590 --> 00:38:25.070
