will enter another body.

00:38:25.070 --> 00:38:27.520
And again, depending on
how we've lived our lives

00:38:27.520 --> 00:38:31.090
and what we've thought
of at the time of death,

00:38:31.090 --> 00:38:37.540
it might be the body of
an animal or a plant.

00:38:37.540 --> 00:38:41.860
And we know that
the atma's there,

00:38:41.860 --> 00:38:45.050
because they're conscious.

00:38:45.050 --> 00:38:48.470
There have been studies
that show, even plants,

00:38:48.470 --> 00:38:50.450
they have consciousness.

00:38:50.450 --> 00:38:52.670
They respond to pain.

00:38:52.670 --> 00:38:57.010
They respond to good music.

00:38:57.010 --> 00:38:58.810
So yes.

00:38:58.810 --> 00:39:04.060
So we should be careful
with any living creature,

00:39:04.060 --> 00:39:06.320
because within that
creature is an atma.

00:39:06.320 --> 00:39:09.510
Just like we're atmas,
they are also atmas,

00:39:09.510 --> 00:39:11.520
but they're in
that kind of body.

